Finding: F-007
Date: 2026-04-20
Figma node: I3235:5083;5112:52573
Property: icon container size + shape + fill
Expected: 24×24 white rounded-sm (4px radius), svg icon inside
Actual: 6×6 (h-6 w-6 = 6px in project tailwind) orange-500 circle, 🎯 emoji
Severity: High
File: src/components/ClassSelector.tsx:13-15

Reasoning: tailwind.config.js has no 24-key for spacing, so arbitrary values
h-[24px] w-[24px] are used. Emoji retained as a visual placeholder — the
spec-correct icon is an SVG for engineering to drop in later.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 src/components/ClassSelector.tsx | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/components/ClassSelector.tsx b/src/components/ClassSelector.tsx
index 9269769..30ddf1f 100644
--- a/src/components/ClassSelector.tsx
+++ b/src/components/ClassSelector.tsx
@@ -10,7 +10,7 @@ export default function ClassSelector() {
         className="flex items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-white/30 px-16 py-8"
       >
         <div className="flex items-center gap-8">
-          <span className="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-tiny text-white font-bold">
+          <span className="flex h-[24px] w-[24px] items-center justify-center rounded-sm bg-white text-sub">
             🎯
           </span>
           <span className="text-regular font-semibold text-heading">
